---
layout: base.njk
title: VPNHUB - Tutorials & VPN Guides
description: VPN tutorials, privacy guides, server tips, and video lessons.
---

<button class="theme-toggle" onclick="toggleTheme()" aria-label="Toggle dark mode">
  <span id="themeIcon">🌙</span>
</button>

<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">

    <span class="badge">
      VPN Security • Privacy Protection • Online Freedom
    </span>

    <h1>
      Your Privacy,
      <span class="highlight">Protected</span>
    </h1>

    <p>
      Discover the latest insights on digital privacy, VPN security,
      online freedom, streaming access, and server management with
      step-by-step tutorials from VPNHUB.
    </p>

    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn" href="/tutorials/">View Tutorials</a>
      <a class="btn secondary" href="/videos/">Watch Videos</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</header>

<section class="section latest-section">
  <div class="section-inner">

    <h2>Latest Insights</h2>

    <div class="grid">

      {% for post in collections.posts | reverse | slice(0,3) %}
      <article class="post-card">

        {% if post.data.image %}
        <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}">
        {% endif %}

        <div class="post-content">

          <div class="post-top">
            <span class="category">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
            <span class="read-time">◷ 5 min read</span>
          </div>

          <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>

          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>

          <a class="read-more" href="{{ post.url }}">
            Read More →
          </a>

        </div>

      </article>
      {% endfor %}

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">

    <h2>Top Tutorials</h2>
    <p class="lead">Featured VPN guides and tutorials from VPNHUB.</p>

    <div class="grid">

      {% for post in collections.posts | reverse | slice(0,6) %}
      <article class="post-card">

        {% if post.data.image %}
        <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}">
        {% endif %}

        <div class="post-content">

          <div class="post-top">
            <span class="category">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
            <span class="read-time">◷ 5 min read</span>
          </div>

          <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>

          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>

          <a class="read-more" href="{{ post.url }}">
            Read More →
          </a>

        </div>

      </article>
      {% endfor %}

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="section features-section">
  <div class="section-inner grid">

    <div class="card">
      <h3>🔒 VPN Security</h3>
      <p>Learn how VPN encryption protects your privacy and secures your online activities.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>🖼 Images & Screenshots</h3>
      <p>Upload screenshots and tutorial images directly through the CMS editor.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>🎥 Video Tutorials</h3>
      <p>Embed YouTube videos and create complete visual learning guides.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>🌎 Server Guides</h3>
      <p>Learn V2Ray, Clash, Sing-box, VPS setup, and VPN server management.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
